long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
CoboVault ethereum extension


Important Note:

1.Cobo Vault has not been officially integrated with MetaMask. It is a proof of concept of extension like Metamask created by the Cobo Vault team. This is an unofficial fork specifically for use with the Cobo Vault. Please use cautiously and report bugs (and feedback!) to support@cobo.com.

2. You should disable your official Metamask extension when using this extension. If you don't, it may result in unexpected behavior.

3. This PoC is forked from the official MetaMask extension. See this fork's source code here.
https://github.com/CoboVault/metamask-extension
